<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#hasMegalithicComponents> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#Menhir> .
