<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#hasTypicalLandscape> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#Landscape> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#hasTypicalLandscape> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has Typical Landscape"@en .
