<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#CulturalLandscapeSite> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A landscape that has been shaped or symbolically interpreted through cultural practices, beliefs, or artistic representation." .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#CulturalLandscapeSite> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Cultural Landscape Site"@en .
