<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#Patron/Promoter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#E39_Actor> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#Patron/Promoter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The sponsor of the archaeological intervention" .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/diniz/ontologies/2024/8/untitled-ontology-30#Patron/Promoter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Patron/Promoter"@en .
